cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

This paper is primarily focused on computer vision tasks, specifically saliency detection and visual classification. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves the use of machine learning techniques, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the use of eye-tracking technology and image datasets suggests that it could also belong to cs.MM (Multimedia) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
